name: Sick&Wonder Limited Edition Pack
description:
Designed as a collection of the 2013 publishings, Sick & Wonder limited edition pack contains both the issue # 8 and the special issue # 9 of CityVision magazine.
Through articles, reports, interviews, the two volumes collect and talk out the annual research dedicated to the "sick and wonder" theme, togheter with a detailed report on the results of the  Rio Cityvision International Competition.

name: Past Shock Limited Edition Pack
description:
Designed as a collection of the 2013 publishings, Past Shock limited edition pack contains both the issue # 5 and issue # 7 of CityVision magazine.
Through articles, reports, interviews, the two volumes collect and talk out the annual research dedicated to the "past shock" theme, togheter with a detailed report on the results of the  New York CityVision International Competition.

name: Cityvision Magazine Collection 2010-2013 (9 issues)
description:
Order your complete Cityvision Magazine Collection (9 issues) celebrating the 4 years publications and get  for free the official 'vintage' bag.

List of the issues:

Issue 1 - Cover by Weekend in a morning
Issue 2 - Cover by Stanley Wood
Issue 3 - Cover by Quayola 
Issue 4 - Cover by Clinton Miller
Issue 5 - Cover by Squint Opera

Issue 7 - Cover by Lash Up

Issue 9 - Cover by Libonati, Ienca, Buzzelli, Galante
